title: Just Burn The Whole RV
itunes:title: Just Burn The Whole RV
description:
Dear Steve and Shirley, I am married to a die-hard football fan and we met in college. We went to an HBCU and for years, we have tailgated with friends and family before the home games. I had a minor surgery so I had to miss the first home game. When we tailgate, we take our RV to the stadium, hook our deep fryer and our grill and get to cooking early in the morning. It’s what we do........................
